headline: TappAlpha Expands ETF Lineup with the Innovation 100 Growth & Daily Income ETF (TDAQ)
summary: As TSPY surpasses $69 million in AUM, TappAlpha launches TDAQ to bring its daily income strategy to the NASDAQ-100. SEATTLE, Sept. 04, 2025 (GLOBE NEWSWIRE) -- TappAlpha, a fintech-powered ETF issuer focused on making advanced investment strategies accessible, announces the launch of the TappAlpha Innovation 100 Growth & Daily Income ETF (Cboe: TDAQ).
